27:24.543 --> 27:25.778
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.
I thought I was lead surgeon.

27:25.812 --> 27:27.013
You are. Okay.

27:27.046 --> 27:28.280
Yes. He...

27:28.314 --> 27:29.982
You can both
be in the surgery.

27:30.016 --> 27:31.951
Okay, let's go.

27:31.984 --> 27:33.619
- Let's go.
- Yeah.

27:33.652 --> 27:36.422
