31:09.668 --> 31:12.004
He has to do everything
his own way.

31:12.038 --> 31:14.273
Did you hire him because
he reminds you of Derek?

31:16.075 --> 31:18.810
No. Not Derek.

31:18.844 --> 31:21.480
He is a mess. He does need
to do things his own way.

31:21.513 --> 31:25.051
Mm-hmm.
But he also has a stroke
of the family genius.

31:25.084 --> 31:27.486
And he's a bit
of a black sheep.

31:27.519 --> 31:28.854
You don't see it, do you?

31:33.892 --> 31:35.394
Is that why
he drives me crazy?

31:35.427 --> 31:38.464
He's me.

31:38.497 --> 31:40.266
Yes, he's you.

31:40.299 --> 31:42.468
He's got the spark.

31:42.501 --> 31:44.203
He's got the drive.

31:44.236 --> 31:46.772
He just needs a chance.

31:46.805 --> 31:50.042
I had to be watched very closely
at that age.

31:50.076 --> 31:51.677
Great.
Are you volunteering?

31:51.710 --> 31:54.346
Because I accept. No,
I was not volunt--

31:54.380 --> 31:55.982
Too late.

