husband wasn't getting a heart.

35:24.356 --> 35:29.094
But I also sewed human flesh
on a living human being,

35:29.127 --> 35:33.232
which was nothing like an orange
and different from a cadaver,

35:33.265 --> 35:34.700
and I think I'm in love
with the whole thing.

35:34.733 --> 35:36.067
That's great.
That's great.

35:36.101 --> 35:39.438
Hey, uh, listen,
this is a little awkward,

35:39.471 --> 35:41.707
but, uh, would you mind
signing this?

35:41.740 --> 35:43.609
What is it?
This is HR paperwork.

35:43.642 --> 35:44.910
It's just so things
don't get muddy.

35:44.943 --> 35:46.612
It just says that
our relationship

35:46.645 --> 35:49.080
