like a stalker?

36:08.800 --> 36:10.001
I'm...

36:10.035 --> 36:11.837
Okay, y-you're
a nice guy, Link,

36:11.870 --> 36:14.540
so let's, um--
let's be friends, hm?

36:28.387 --> 36:29.555
Oh, my God.

36:30.822 --> 36:31.790
Oh, my God.

36:33.892 --> 36:35.694
Ms. Milton!
Mm-hmm?

36:35.727 --> 36:37.996
Ms. Milton,
Marina is awake.

36:46.004 --> 36:48.607
You did it!

36:48.640 --> 36:49.675
You hoped.

36:51.343 --> 36:53.178
I hoped.

36:53.211 --> 36:56.147
Oh, baby.

36:59.351 --> 37:01.520
Oh.

37:03.121 --> 37:04.390
Oh.

37:04.423 --> 37:06.124
It's okay.

37:06.157 --> 37:08.694
How's that dark sense of humor
working out, Yasuda?

37:17.836 --> 37:18.470
Okay, good.
Good, good, good.

37:20.739 --> 37:22.774
Okay, good.

37:22.808 --> 37:24.676
Am I a tree?

37:26.077 --> 37:27.679
I'm sorry,
are you a what, now?

37:27.713 --> 37:29.581
Uh, not yet, Sarah.

37:30.782 --> 37:32.284
Can I see my kids?

37:32.318 --> 37:33.552
Uh, no, Sarah, not yet.

37:33.585 --> 37:35.186
Y-You need to rest
and recover,

37:35.220 --> 37:37.923
and in a couple days,
we can talk about it.

37:37.956 --> 37:39.525
Okay?

37:41.960 --> 37:44.262
I want to thank the donor...
* Slowly

37:44.296 --> 37:46.798
Mm-hmm.
...family.

37:46.832 --> 37:48.534
Someone's child died.

37:48.567 --> 37:50.268
♪ I'm becoming steadfast

37:50.302 --> 37:53.271
I want to tell them
I know what they lost.

37:53.305 --> 37:55.106
Of course.
I understand, but, really...

37:55.140 --> 37:56.742
you do need to rest.

37:56.775 --> 37:58.910
And then we'll talk
about it more. Oh.

37:58.944 --> 38:00.879
Okay?

38:00.912 --> 38:02.314
Okay.

38:02.348 --> 38:04.249
♪ Part of me
is far from ready ♪

38:04.282 --> 38:06.117
♪ To come back

38:07.853 --> 38:11.690
♪ I don't want to be
the last one chosen ♪

38:13.725 --> 38:16.127
Uh, you feel alright,
Dr. Griffith?

38:16.161 --> 38:20.799
♪ I don't wanna be the source
