38:22.267 --> 38:25.504
Um, I'm so sorry, um...

38:25.537 --> 38:28.239
do you need a grief counselor,
a pastor, or--

38:28.273 --> 38:31.777
She died when I was born. Oh.

38:31.810 --> 38:37.182
In this hospital, so I haven't
been here since then.

38:37.215 --> 38:38.584
Since you were born?

38:38.617 --> 38:40.419
I haven't been here
since the birth of me

