killed my mother somewhere
in one of these rooms,

38:42.488 --> 38:44.590
which is why I was late
my first day.

38:44.623 --> 38:46.257
It had nothing to do
with the tornado.

38:46.291 --> 38:48.794
I had a... panic attack,

38:48.827 --> 38:51.597
and then I saw
the color of the walls.

38:51.630 --> 38:54.132
I've been...

38:54.165 --> 38:56.935
picturing this place
my whole life.

38:56.968 --> 38:58.837
When I think of my mother
and the walls are beige,

38:58.870 --> 39:01.239
and then I get here and
they're blue, and it's just...

39:04.943 --> 39:09.047
...disorienting, disappointing.

39:11.082 --> 39:12.551
Got it wrong all this time.

39:12.584 --> 39:14.319
♪ Soon there'll be
still waters ♪

39:14.352 --> 39:17.823
Well, they only painted
the walls blue a few years ago.

39:17.856 --> 39:19.224
You got it right.

39:19.257 --> 39:20.358
♪ Soon there'll be
still waters ♪

39:23.562 --> 39:25.230
♪ Soon there'll be
still waters ♪

39:25.263 --> 39:27.232
Makes me feel so--

39:27.265 --> 39:30.669
so much better.

39:30.702 --> 39:32.471
Thank you.
Thank you, Dr. Webber.

39:32.504 --> 39:33.905
Of course.

39:33.939 --> 39:35.140
And I'm sorry that I was late
on my first day

39:35.173 --> 39:36.575
and I lied about why.

39:36.608 --> 39:37.909
It's understandable,
Dr. Griffith.

39:37.943 --> 39:39.511
It won't happen again.

39:42.881 --> 39:45.817
♪ Soon there'll be
