on purpose.

40:00.599 --> 40:02.400
Don't hate me.
I needed a laugh.

40:02.434 --> 40:04.335
So glad I could provide it.

40:04.369 --> 40:07.338
Hi.
Keep walking, Schmitt,
we're not on speaking terms.

40:10.241 --> 40:11.643
Harsh.

40:11.677 --> 40:14.145
Yeah, well, I can be mean
when I want to be.

40:14.179 --> 40:15.747
Oh, I know.

40:21.119 --> 40:22.353
Okay.

40:26.357 --> 40:27.826
Come in.

40:27.859 --> 40:29.394
Hey. Uh...

40:29.427 --> 40:31.162
Hey.
Thank you for that.

40:31.196 --> 40:32.731
I-I've been at this
a long time,

40:32.764 --> 40:36.301
and I've never done a triple,
so thank you.

40:36.334 --> 40:37.536
How's Sarah?

40:37.569 --> 40:40.472
Well, she's not a tree.

40:40.506 --> 40:42.474
Sorry, yeah, she's good.
She's good.

40:42.508 --> 40:44.142
S-She's awake,
and she's grateful.

40:44.175 --> 40:46.645
That's excellent news.
It is.

40:48.747 --> 40:50.816
Okay, I'm gonna go.

40:50.849 --> 40:52.217
Or don't.

40:53.952 --> 40:55.053
Or don't.

40:55.086 --> 40:57.388
I need
a residency director.

40:57.422 --> 40:59.090
<i>New beginnings
aren't always easy.</i>

40:59.124 --> 41:01.259
You're the best teacher
I know.

41:01.292 --> 41:04.262
This class is a lot like
you were at their age.

41:04.295 --> 41:07.165
They either didn't match
anywhere else

41:07.198 --> 41:08.800
or got kicked out
of their programs.

41:08.834 --> 41:10.636
So, they're-- they're
diamonds in the rough--

41:10.669 --> 41:12.137
is that what you're saying?

41:12.170 --> 41:14.405
Yes, and I think that
I would have never hired them

41:14.439 --> 41:16.441
if I didn't know you
and I didn't know your story.

41:16.474 --> 41:18.376
I think you inspired
this whole thing.

41:19.778 --> 41:21.412
And I need
a residency director.

41:21.446 --> 41:23.982
It's excellent pay, and you
wouldn't have to travel as much,

41:24.015 --> 41:26.384
and I...would love it

41:26.417 --> 41:29.287
if you would
just at least consider it.

41:29.320 --> 41:30.889
<i>When you get a new organ,</i>

41:30.922 --> 41:32.558
<i>you spend your life
on medications</i>

41:32.591 --> 41:34.960
<i>designed to suppress
your immune system</i>

41:34.993 --> 41:37.095
<i>so that your body
won't reject it.</i>

41:39.364 --> 41:40.331
Hi.

41:40.365 --> 41:41.733
Hey.
Hey.

41:41.767 --> 41:44.035
You're here.
Yeah, you called and we came.

41:44.069 --> 41:45.604
Hey.

41:45.637 --> 41:48.073
Right, but, I mean, I--
I did call you three weeks ago.

41:48.106 --> 41:50.408
Well, I couldn't work
three weeks ago, but now I can.

41:50.441 --> 41:52.544
Sort of.
Not sort of. I can.

41:52.578 --> 41:54.045
Well, he has
to be supervised.

41:54.079 --> 41:55.714
You don't have to say it
like that.

41:55.747 --> 41:56.982
Well, how do you want me
to say it, Owen?

41:57.015 --> 41:58.650
You're very tan.
Well, yeah,

41:58.684 --> 41:59.885
Thank you.
