surfing every day

41:59.918 --> 42:01.553
with a 24-year-old
named Stella

42:01.587 --> 42:03.655
while we've been paying out
our entire life savings

42:03.689 --> 42:06.457
to a $1,700-an-hour
attorney.

42:06.491 --> 42:09.795
Yeah. And she's been drinking
rosé angrily all day,

42:09.828 --> 42:11.462
but you don't see me
criticizing her, so.

42:11.496 --> 42:14.365
Wow.
Uh, I'm gonna go.

42:14.399 --> 42:15.834
But you will
think about it?

42:15.867 --> 42:17.669
Yeah,
I'll think about it.

42:19.404 --> 42:21.607
<i>But at least you have
a life to spend...</i>

42:21.640 --> 42:22.941
Let's sit down. Great.

42:22.974 --> 42:24.676
Yes, yes.
<i>...and a body to medicate.</i>

42:24.710 --> 42:29.280
So, the attorney got all
criminal charges dropped.

42:29.314 --> 42:31.282
For the low, low price
of a quarter million dollars.

42:31.316 --> 42:32.684
Wow, okay.

42:32.718 --> 42:34.485
So do you have
a medical license?

42:34.519 --> 42:36.154
W--
A suspended
medical license.

42:36.187 --> 42:38.857
I just have to be supervised
for a little while.

42:38.890 --> 42:40.125
How long is a little while?

42:40.158 --> 42:41.359
Not that long.

42:41.392 --> 42:43.228
Six months is that long, Owen.

42:45.764 --> 42:46.998
Yeah, six months.

42:48.566 --> 42:50.468
<i>Second chances can feel
like an insult</i>

42:50.501 --> 42:52.938
<i>if you can't get over what you
lost the first time around.</i>

42:52.971 --> 42:53.939
My eyes hurt.

42:53.972 --> 42:54.940
♪ Go

42:54.973 --> 42:56.708
Everything hurts.

42:56.742 --> 42:58.877
I think
my fingernails hurt.

42:58.910 --> 43:00.712
Not mine.
I feel high.

43:00.746 --> 43:03.181
Saving lives is the most
epic high.

43:03.214 --> 43:04.950
That's adrenaline.
Plus dopamine.

43:04.983 --> 43:07.518
Eh, I prefer to think of it
as magic.

43:07.552 --> 43:08.887
♪ Go, listen to the morning

43:08.920 --> 43:10.121
What do they call you,
Griffith?

43:10.155 --> 43:11.623
♪ Go be still
among the trees ♪

43:11.657 --> 43:13.191
Simone.

43:13.224 --> 43:14.860
What, no nickname?

